vocabulary.description: marine andtTerrestrial geographical region. Terrestrial terms are compatible with the TDWG GeographicalRegions LSID vocabulary (http://rs.tdwg.org/ontology/voc/GeographicRegion.rdf). The terrestrial regions are structured in a hierarchy having four levels of detail. Marine areas terms and hierarchie are conform with BioBEL marine area classification (http://biobel.biodiversity.be/biobel/search/classification)
